flowchart LR
    A["Raw data N samples × P features"] --> B["`Standardize (zero mean, unit variance)`"]
    B --> C["`Compute covariance matrix (P × P)`"]
    C --> D["`Eigen-decompose → eigenvectors & eigenvalues`"]
    D --> E["`Sort by explained variance (scree plot)`"]
    E --> F{How many components?}
    F -->|"Keep k where cumulative variance ≥ 95%"| G["Project onto top-k principal components"]
    G --> H["Reduced data N samples × k"]
    H --> I["`Visualise (k=2/3) or feed into model`"]
